string short(int dark)
 
        Gives the short description of the object.  This is what is used
as the singular inventory of objects and used most of the time when telling
the user about an object.  The objects quiet often do processing of the
short descrtion when it get to here.  For the unadulterated short use
query_short
 
See also
    pretty_short, long, query_plural, pretty_plural, query_short
